1 arising from the taxpayer's modified gross receipts tax base under
2 section 203. The adjustment under subsection (2)(i) shall must be
3 calculated without regard to the federal effect of the deduction.
4 If the adjustment under subsection (2)(i) is greater than the
5 taxpayer's business income tax base, any adjustment that is unused
6 may be carried forward and applied as an adjustment to the
7 taxpayer's business income tax base before apportionment in future
